Please see tweets below for six other alternative routes to use during the closure. Some options may be less crowded than using the 97 Yonge bus.
As an alternative, customers at St Clair Station can use the 512 St Clair Streetcar westbound and transfer to the 5 Avenue Road or travel to St Clair West Station to go southbound on Line 1.
As an alternative, customers at Eglinton Station can use the 5 Avenue Road from the bus bay and travel south to Museum or Queens Park Stations on Line 1.
As an alternative, customers at Eglinton Station can use the 32 Eglinton West to travel westbound to Eglinton West Station to access Line 1.
As an alternative, customers at Lawrence Station can use the 52 Lawrence West to travel westbound to Lawrence West Station to access Line 1.
As an alternative, customers at York Mills can use the 96 Wilson or 165 Weston Road north to travel westbound to Wilson Station to access Line 1.
As an alternative, customers at Sheppard Station can use the 84 Sheppard West to travel westbound to Sheppard West Station to access Line 1.
